{
  "text": "In the last decades, the Lattice Boltzmann (LB) method is considered versus classical approaches to solve complex problems of heat and fluid flow [CITATION_1] - [CITATION_2] . Its time-dependent scheme is in accordance with unsteady plasma jet nature. In addition, the LB equation is particularly (fundamentally) adopted to simulating gas flows, which present a collisional process.",
  "citation_candidates": [
